<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　传统中药方剂及针灸等方面的特色，特别是药物方面的使用经验。这些，若能充分加以发掘利用，将有利于中医学的长足发展。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Characteristics of acupuncture and traditional Chinese medicine prescription, especially with regard to drug use experience. These, if we can fully explore the use will contribute to the rapid development of Chinese medicine.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">73</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　具体而言，中医学的优势，最值得重视的大约有四部分： 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　In particular, the advantages of traditional Chinese medicine, the most noteworthy about four parts:
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">74</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　（一）辨证论治的丰富内涵
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　（１）Richness of treatment based on syndrome differentiation
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">75</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　中医学的辨证论治，是一行之有效的治疗学体系，她着眼于机体特定状态(包括生理、病理状态)的调整，并借此达到治疗的目的，她与西医学的对抗性或替代性治疗思路异曲同工。而几千年来的不断探索、积累，又使中医学在这方面拥有丰富而又行之有效的临床经验，确凿的临床疗效。中医学之所以能经历西方近现代医学的冲击，近年来呈现出强劲的复兴之势，就是由于她拥有独特的调整纠治思路和确凿的疗效。诸如心脑血管疾病、肿瘤等的治疗中，中医学都展现出她独有的优势。比如，对于老年肿瘤的治疗，中医倡导“零毒化疗”，带病生存，疗效卓著。有人报导，75 岁以上高龄患者 453 例，纯以中药治疗为主，其中健健康康地活过 3 年的人占了 2/3；又如对西医各种疗法都不敏感的癌中之王────胰腺癌的纯中医治疗，也获得了令人折服的结果，存活期超过 5 年的接近 40%。即便是令整个社会束手无策的SARS，配合中医药，也能明显地降低死亡率，提高治愈率，且确保了生存质量。在现代种种“瘟疫”的防治中，中医学仍将发挥其无以替代的作用。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Treatment based on syndrome differentiation in traditional Chinese medicine, is an effective treatment system, she focused on the specific State of the body (includes physiological, pathological conditions) adjustments, and to achieve the purpose of treatment, her confrontation with the Western medicine or alternative treatment with similar. Thousands of years of continuous exploration and accumulation and TCM have abundant clinical experience, and proven, solid clinical effects. Is able to experience the impact of modern Western medicine in traditional Chinese medicine, presents a strong revival of the trend in recent years, is that she has a unique adjustment correction and corroborative effect. Such as in the treatment of cardiovascular and cerebrovascular diseases, cancer and other and exhibit her unique advantages of traditional Chinese medicine. For example, for treatment of tumors in the elderly medicine advocating "zero HIV chemotherapy" humans to survive, the curative effect is outstanding. Some reports, senior citizens over the age of 75 patients with 453 cases, pure is dominated by traditional Chinese medicine, in which healthy people live longer than 3 years account for two-thirds, and if any Western medical treatments are not sensitive to cancer-pancreatic cancer-the King of pure Chinese medicine treatment, also get a convincing result, survival time than three years closer to 5. Even if the entire community to stop SARS, Combined with traditional Chinese medicine, can significantly reduce mortality rates, improve the cure rate, and ensures that the quality of life. In modern times all kinds of "plague" in combat, will still play its irreplaceable role in traditional Chinese medicine.  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">76</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　此外，中医治疗学以辨证论治为原则，以扶正祛邪，调整阴阳为核心，通过调动人自身的抗病能力(正气)，协调内在机能活动，以达到祛病除邪，却病强身的目的。如此获得的疗效常是持久且十分稳定的，故有人认定中医学是“治本”的。再者，中医治疗学又重视机体的个性差异，主张因人、因时、因地制宜，发展形成了一整套治则和治法，并以针刺方药等丰富手段来贯彻上述治则治法。显然，这一诊治体系不仅更适合于解决多因素、多层次的慢性及综合性疾病治疗问题。而且，也适合于诸如亚健康的调整，一些心身疾病及精神障碍等的治疗。因此，在临床上，有着数千年间积累发展起来的辨证论治体系及丰富诊治经验的中医学，有着明显的优势。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　In addition, therapy with treatment based on syndrome differentiation of traditional Chinese medicine on the principle of strengthening healthy Qi, regulation of yin and Yang as the core, through the mobilization of human resistance (righteousness) to coordinate internal functional activities to achieve the illnesses evil, strong purpose. So obtained is often lasting effect and is very stable, so it was found that traditional Chinese medicine is "root". Moreover, differences in personality and TCM treatment of attention to the body, when advocates for the people, because, according to development formed a set of governance and methods and prescriptions, such as means of implementing the principle of acupuncture therapy. It is clear that This system of diagnosis and treatment more appropriate to solve a number of factors, not only multi-level and integrated chronic disease treatments. Moreover, it is suitable for such as sub-healthy adjustment, some treatment of psychosomatic diseases and mental disorders. Therefore, clinically, with its thousands of years accumulation development system and rich experience in the diagnosis and treatment based on syndrome differentiation in traditional Chinese medicine, there is a clear advantage.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">77</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　（二）源自天然的中药之长及讲究配伍的方剂之优
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　（２）Nature long and pay attention to the compatibility of prescription of traditional Chinese medicine
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">78</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　中药中动、植物类药占大半。从生物进化史来看，人类经历了由无生命的元素到有生命的细胞，从单细胞生物到多细胞生物，从单器官生物到多器官生物的演变过程。在这条进化长链中，动、植物与人类的进化层次远较化学合成制品更接近，它们的组成都是蛋白质、氨基酸、生物碱、鞣酸等有机物。中药具有治疗意义的生物属性是通过人体与自然环境进行物质、能量、信息交换等因素的接触过程中发挥作用的。所以，大多药性平和，副作用小，不干扰人体正常的生理过程，有的具有食治共存的双重作用，故历来有“药食同源”之说。特别是通过数千年实践验证发展起来的方剂配伍理论，用以指导用药，可以产生各个单味中药所没有的，同时也不是各单味药物功效简单叠加所能产生的整体功效。因此，不仅效果理想，而且有着深入发掘的巨大潜力。相反，化学合成为主的西药，在取得疗效进展的同时，其副作用和毒理作用也成倍增加。合成药物致毒、致畸、致癌甚至致死的情况日渐增多，以致形成“药源性疾病”、“药源性公害”等严重医学问题，引起了人们的震惊与重视，因此，一大批化学药物的医疗价值被间接否定了。举例来说，化疗药物至今仍是西医学治疗肿瘤的全身疗法中的唯一可靠手段，但它毒性每每令人不寒而慄。许多肿瘤患者其实是死于化疗药物的，这是西方医学的无奈。然而，人们从天然中药中提取出某种多糖结构和三萜酸成分，以特定比例配伍成中药制剂，用于各种肿瘤的治疗，不仅未见毒副反应，相反，通过诱导癌细胞自然凋亡和癌变细胞的进一步分化，造成了大量的癌细胞死亡，却不伤及正常组织细胞。这就促使人们重新认识自然界的内在魅力。此现实已敦促医药学家把注意力转向自然界，转向天然的动、植物药类。“回到大自然”，“回到中医药中去”，已成为国内外医药学界一种越来越普遍和强烈的呼声。有的学者甚至认为中药学是建立世界统一的新药学的基础。可见，在药物学方面中医学也有巨大优势。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Half of animal and plant medicine in traditional Chinese medicine. Judging from the biological evolution, elements of human experience from the inanimate to living cells, from a unicellular organism of multicellular organisms, from single organs organisms to multiple organs of biological evolution. In this long chain of evolution, animal, plant and human evolution closer to levels much higher than chemical synthesis products, their composition was protein, amino acids, alkaloids, tannic acid and other organic compounds. Treated by Chinese herbs with interesting biological properties are passed to humans and the natural environment for matter, energy, information exchange exposure and other factors play a role in the process. Therefore, most mild temperament, side effects, Does not interfere with normal physiological processes of the human body, has the dual role of dietetic therapy coexistence, it has always been "medicinal and edible," said. Especially developed through thousands of years of field-proven prescription theory to guide drug use can result in single herb does not have, but also not a single drug efficacy of simple overlay that can be produced by the overall effectiveness. Thus, not only the results are satisfactory, and the enormous potential of deep excavations. Instead, the chemical compound consisting mainly of Western medicine, in the effect of the progress made at the same time, its side effects and toxicity is also multiplied. Toxic synthetic drugs, teratogenic, carcinogenic and even death from increasing Form a "drug-induced diseases", "drug-induced hazards" and other serious medical problems, has aroused alarm and attention, so the medical value of a large number of chemical substances have been indirectly denied. For example, chemotherapy drugs remained a Western medicine therapy for systemic cancer therapy and the only reliable means of toxicity but it is not cold and 慄. Many cancer patients die of chemotherapy drugs, which is the frustration of Western medicine. However, it is extracted from natural herbs out of some sort of triterpene acids polysaccharide structure and component, in particular Wu Cheng blending preparation proportion, used for the treatment of various tumors, not only no toxic side effects, on the contrary, By inducing apoptosis in cancer cells naturally and further differentiation of cancerous cells, causing the deaths of a large number of cancer cells without harming normal cells. This prompted people to rediscover nature's inherent charm. This reality has urged medicine turned his attention to the natural world, turn to natural animal and plant medicine. "Back to nature", "go back to Chinese medicine" has become the more common medicine at home and abroad and a strong voice. Some researchers even believe that TCM new drugs is to establish world unity Foundation. We can see in the pharmacology of traditional Chinese medicine also has an enormous advantage.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">79</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　（三）一些理论认识之潜在科学价值
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　（３）The potential scientific value of some theoretical understanding 
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">80</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　与其他传统医学不同，中医学是有其系统理论阐述的，这些理论阐述虽还与现代科学理论有些差异，却包含了许多值得重视的科学苗头，有可能成为新的重大科学理论的初级形态。比如，中医的经络学说就是典型例子，他描述了客观而实在的“循经感传”现象，尽管不够精确，却也远胜于西方医学对客观事实所不允许的偏见或忽视；又如关于心身关系，中医学也有着丰富而深刻的阐述，人们在心身医学探讨中日益取材于古代中医学家的智慧。再如，中医学关于内伤病因目的理性阐述，可成为今天归纳健康危险因素中生活与行为因素的范本。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Different from other traditional medicine, there is a system of traditional Chinese medicine theory on these theories and modern scientific theories set out some differences, but contains a lot of important science set in, has the potential to become a major new primary speciation of a scientific theory. Like, TCM of Meridian doctrine is typical examples, he description has objective and is of "through by sense pass" phenomenon, despite enough precise, is also far than Western medical on objective facts by not allows of bias or ignored; and as on psychosomatic relationship, TCM also has rich and deep of described, people in psychosomatic medical discussion in the increasingly based Yu ancient in the medical home of wisdom. As another example, Objective rationality elaborated on traditional Chinese medicine of internal injuries etiology can be summarized health risk factors and behavioral factors in today's models.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">81</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　（四）非药物疗法之长及分支学科的潜在优势
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　（４）The potential advantages of non-drug therapies and the branches
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">82</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　针灸、推拿、外熏、熏洗、浸泡、食疗等传统的非药物内服治疗方法，具有疗效确凿，简便易行之特点，深受欢迎。笔者便善于运用外敷法治疗癌症性因素或肝硬化引起的顽固性胸腹水，疗效显著。有一例高血压患者出现危象，血压高达 240/160mmHg，服用了各种化学降压药，包括静推降压药，均无效， 随时有可能出意外，十分危险。我们以外用法浸泡双脚引火归源，20 多分钟后，症状改善，一个半小时后，血压降至 160/100mmHg，危险解除，日后病人再用此法也是屡试不爽。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>Acupuncture, massage, smoke, smoke outside wash, soak, therapeutic and other traditional methods of non-drug treatment, has the effect of conclusive, user-friendly features, is most welcome. The author is very good at using the application in the treatment of cancer or cirrhosis obstinate hydrothorax and ascites caused by, the curative effect is significant. A crisis occurred in patients with hypertension, the blood pressure up to 240/160mmHg, taking various chemical blood-pressure pills, including static push blood pressure medicine, are valid, and have the potential to surprise at any time, is dangerous. Soaking my feet and return fire outside the US usage sources, more than 20 minutes later, symptoms improve, 1.5 hours later, Blood pressure fell to 160/100mmHg, dangerous discharge patients using this method was tried again in the future.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">83</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　此外，在诸多分支学科中，中医学也优势明显，如心身医学领域，中医学有着系统的理论认识和独特的精神情志疗法；在健康医学方面，中医学既形成了独具风格的“四气调神”，摄生养性等许多科学内容，又创造出气功、太极拳、八段锦等行之有效的强身保健措施；在老年医学和营养学(食疗、药膳学)方面，中医学更可谓素来重视，并摸索和积累了精彩的内容和丰富的方法；对病后调理将息的一系列措施将有助于康复医学外延的进一步扩大和内涵的不断充实。此外，在诸如社会医学、时间医学(时间治疗学)、气象医学、地理医学等领域，中医学也或多或少地具有一些杰出思想和切实可行的方法。对于这些领域潜在特长的开发，将促进中医学和这些分支学科以致整个医学科学的进步。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Also, in many branch discipline in the, TCM also advantage obviously, as psychosomatic medical area, TCM has system of theory awareness and unique of spirit love Chi therapy; in health medical aspects, TCM both formed has unique style of "four gas adjustable God", photo who gave birth to sexual, many science content, and created out qigong, and taijiquan, and eight paragraph Kam, proven of body health measures; in old medical and nutrition (therapeutic, and medicinal learn) aspects, TCM more can be described as has always been attention, And groping and have accumulated wonderful and rich; diseases Reserch on the rest of a series of measures will contribute to further expansion of the outreach of rehabilitation medicine and continuously enrich the connotation. In addition, in areas such as social medicine, medicine (chronotherapy), meteorology, geography, medicine, and other fields of medicine, traditional Chinese medicine also has some good ideas and more or less realistic way. For these potential strengths in the areas of development, and these branches will promote medical disciplines so that the progress of medical science as a whole.  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">84</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　上世纪 70 年代末，世界卫生组织提出了“到 2000 年人人健康’的全球性战略目标，可惜未能实现。在我们看来，要实现这一目标，前提犹是要“人人享受保健’。现在，一些国家的卫生经费虽一路猛增，但实际效益却不明显。为此，改变目前人类保健模式，并扩大规模，成了卫生事业发展的世界性趋势。而要适应新的保健模式，达到人人享受保健的目标，经济、有效而可行的手段就是天然药物及针灸推拿和保健措施的应用。尽管全世界目前有数以万计的现代化药厂，然就其在“人人享受保健”这一伟大事业中的意义而言，是难以与天然药物及针灸推拿媲美的。因此，世界卫生组织远见卓识地把中国的针灸学列为发展重点。这也是中医学的一个优势。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　The late 70, by the World Health Organization, "health for all by 2000 ' global strategic goals, unfortunately, did not materialize. In our opinion, to achieve this goal, the premise is "health care for all '. Now, while some national health expenditure surged all the way, but the actual benefit is not obvious. To do this, change the current patterns for human health, and to expand the size, became the worldwide trends of development of health service. To adapt to new models of care, and achieve the objective of health for all, economic, effective and practical means for natural medicines and acupuncture and massage and the application of health measures. Although today there are literally thousands of modern pharmaceutical companies in the world, and its "health for all" this great business sense, are difficult to compare favourably with natural medicine and acupuncture. Therefore, the World Health Organization vision of Chinese Acupuncture and moxibustion as development priorities. This is one advantage of traditional Chinese medicine.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">85</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>二、 中医学的危机与不足 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>２．Crisis and deficiency in traditional Chinese medicine  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">86</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　作为 21 世纪的中医学人才，头脑必须是清晰，冷静的，分析必须是理性的。现时代的中医学，也有着众多不利于其生存或发展的因素，甚至可以说存在着不少生存危机。这些包括： 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　As Chinese medicine talents of the 21st century, the mind must be clear, calm, analysis must be rational. Modern traditional Chinese medicine, also has a number of negative factors on the survival and development of, and can even say there is a lot of existential crisis. These include:
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">87</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　中国传统文化固有的尖锐的两重性，及其中消极、保守成分对中医学的巨大束缚作用；要发展中医学，首先须深刻全面反思传统文化； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Sharp dualism inherent in traditional Chinese culture, and its negative and conservative constituents of traditional Chinese medicine in great bondage role to develop traditional Chinese medicine, must first be impressed overall reflections on the traditional culture;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">88</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　独特理论体系的封闭结构阻碍了学科的顺利发展；为此，突破原有理论体系是发展中医学的关键；
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Unique theoretical system of enclosed structure hindered the smooth development of the discipline; to that end, breaking the original theory is the key to the development of traditional Chinese medicine;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">89</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　作为传统科学，它对信息社会中“知识激增”等冲击，适应性差，难以迅速吸收、容纳和利用新的信息及新的技术设备和方法手段，为此，造就一大批具有现代科学素质的人才堪称当务之急； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　As a traditional science, which in the information society "knowledge explosion" impact, flexible, rapid absorption, fit and use of new information and new technology equipment and methods, for which makes a large number of modern scientific quality talent is the priority;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">90</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　中医学的许多认识和思想尽管可谓天才的、杰出的，但又是粗糙的、笼统的；正确性高、准确性低；且大多无法用现代科学手段加以研究（缺乏可证伪性），如不对这些人类认识的“粗产品”加以科学提炼，中医学将永远踏步不前； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Despite many beliefs and ideas of Chinese medicine can be described as a genius, outstanding, but rough, General, and high accuracy, low accuracy, and were largely unable to use modern scientific methods to study (lack of falsification), as these human knowledge not "rough" refined science, Chinese medicine will always step forward;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">91</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　方法论和方法虽有某些特色，但却与现代科学方法论存在着时代的差距； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Methodology and methods have certain features, but there is a disparity in the age of modern scientific methodology;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">92</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　尽管中医临床疗效确凿，但诊治过程大多只是建立在感性的经验基础之上；许多只知其然，不知其所以然，有着一定的“偶然性”； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Although conclusive clinical therapeutic effect of traditional Chinese medicine, but most of the treatment process is based on perceptual experience; many know only the result, but I do not know why, has some "accidental";
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">93</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　在一些新兴分支学科中的经验和知识只有相对的意义，如不及时加以发掘和发展，随着现代研究的面上铺开和点上深入，这些认识的意义很快将不复存在； 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Experience and knowledge in the emerging subfield is only relative significance, if not timely discovery and development, with the modern study of spread out on the surface and in depth, meaning these perceptions will soon no longer exist;
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">94</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　最为关键的是中医理论自身的缺陷，许多基本概念含糊不清，且不少是无法证伪的哲学术语之移植；对这类概念的内涵和外延若不清晰地予以确定，那么，要发展中医只能是纸上谈兵，因为明确概念是共同进行任何科学研究的前提和出发点。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Most critical is the theory of traditional Chinese medicine's own shortcomings, many of the basic concepts are vague, and many of the philosophical terminology of graft cannot be falsified; if the concepts of connotation and denotation of this kind is not clearly identified, then, to develop traditional Chinese medicine can only be empty talk, because a concept is common to any of the prerequisite and starting point for scientific research. 
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">95</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　上述这些分析，主要是从学科自身出发的，一个学科的发展与停滞，尚有其外在的因素，是内外多因素综合作用之果。就外因来看，以下几点最堪称忧：
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　These analyses, mainly starting from the subject itself, a discipline development and stagnation, there are external factors, is the fruit of the combined effect of multiple factors both inside and outside. External view, worry-most are following several points:
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">96</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　(1)临床阵地萎缩 由于中医学诊断手段是传统的，有很高的科学价值，但却与现代科学几无一致，说理难通；加上服药麻烦、药价上涨、道地药材奇缺、疗程较长、药味苦涩等一系列因素，使民众中自然而然地形成了“急性病看西医，慢性病找中医”、“西医院诊断，中医院治疗”等观念，使一大批病员涌入综合性医院，求治于中医者减少。在中西医学对峙的形势下，中医临床阵地有所萎缩。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　(1) clinical positions atrophy due to TCM diagnosis means is traditional of, has is high of science value, but is and modern science several no consistent, reasoning hard pass; plus medication trouble, and drug price rose, and authentic herbs scarce, and treatments more long, and medicine bitter, series factors, makes people in the naturally to formed has "acute see Western, chronic disease found TCM", and "West hospital diagnosis, in the hospital treatment", concept, makes a large number of patient influx integrated hospital, begged treatment Yu TCM who reduced. In the context of confrontation between Western and Chinese medicine, TCM clinical positions have shrunk. 
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">97</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　(2)医药失序 中医学系统中，理论源于医生实践，而药物又是医家实践的重要手段。药、医、理三者相互关联，表现出明显的有序性。而如今，药物被视作单纯的商品而其生产只注重经济效益，以致出现了常用药物野生资源日趋减少，药源危机；药品质量下降，炮制粗劣、品种混乱、以假乱真，管理和加工危机；加上使用中种种令人费解的人为因素，煎服时的不遵医嘱、不讲究时间和火候等因素都影响了疗效，而这一切可归之为医药失序。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　(2) medical disorder in the system of traditional Chinese medicine, the theory stems from medical practice, drugs are important means of medical practice. Drugs, medicine, science linkages between these three, showed significant order. And now, drug was depending on for simple of merchandise and its production only focused on statistics, that appeared has common drug wild resources increasingly reduced, drug source crisis; drug quality declined, concoction cheap, and varieties chaos, and entrusts, management and processing crisis; plus using in the various was puzzling of artificial factors, fried clothing Shi of not compliance orders, and not about time and heat, factors are effects has effect, and this all can return of for medicine disorder.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">98</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　(3)中医教育的尴尬 现时代，一方面，社会需要大批有水平、有造诣的中医人才；另一方面，中医人才培养又存在一些问题，他的成长需要一个过程。这就使中医教育陷入了一种尴尬的境地中：一方面，中医院校无法吸收大量学生入学，特别是一些有志于斯者；另一方面，已毕业的学生纷纷改行。中医教育工作者应该怎样让计算机、基因工程和核技术时代的青年学生对中医学真正发生浓厚兴趣，然后孜孜不倦地去学习、掌握它，进而全身心地热爱它，发展它？要知道，回避问题才是最可悲的，因此，这是放在中医教育工作者面前，亟待通过系统改革加以解决的生存难题。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　(3) the embarrassment of modern Chinese medicine education, on the one hand, society needs a large number of levels, and accomplished professionals of Chinese medicine, on the other, training professionals of Chinese medicine and there are some problems, a process necessary for his growth. This makes the education of Chinese medicine in an awkward position: on the one hand, cannot absorb large numbers of students in TCM colleges, especially those interested in, on the other, of graduated students are diverted. Chinese medicine educators how to let computers, genetic engineering and technology students in the age of real interest in traditional Chinese medicine, and the dedication to learning and mastering it, Then commit yourself to loving it, develop it? You know, begs the question is the most tragic, therefore, that is put in front of practitioners of Chinese medicine education, need to be addressed through system reform to survive challenges.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">99</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　上述这些不足或危机，大多是可以通过发展和变革，加以克服或超越。医药适时是个管理加技术改进问题，教育是个变革旧体制，革新旧的教育方法，以适应新环境的问题，所有这一切，首先要求现时代的中医师，有与时俱进的时代精神，勇于创新，勇于前进，以发展的姿态、进取的精神，以及综合的科学方法，来克服传统中医学中的一些不足或危机。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　These are inadequate or crisis, mostly through the development and transformation, overcoming or transcendence. Medicine timely is a management plus technology improved problem, education is a change old institutional, innovations old of education method, to adapted new environment of problem, all this all, first requires now era of practitioners, has times of era spirit, bravely innovation, bravely forward, to development of attitude, and aggressive of spirit, and integrated of science method, to overcome traditional TCM in the of some insufficient or crisis.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">100</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>第四节 拓展中医生存新空间 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>Section 4 Expanding new space for survival of traditional Chinese medicine
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">101</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　学术也有一个生存空间问题，特别是在现代科学与西医学夹缝中生存的中医学，其生存空间问题尤其重要。其实，上一节所谈的许多不足或中医学的缺陷，大多都涉及了学科生存与发展的空间问题。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Also has a living space, particularly in modern science and traditional Chinese medicine and Western medical survival in the crevice, and space issues of particular importance to their survival. In fact, the previous section talked about many deficiencies or shortcomings of traditional Chinese medicine, mostly relate to the survival and development of the discipline of space issues.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">102</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　我们认为：中医不啻是旧的、传统的；也是新的、富有生气的。因为对于西医学来说，从视野到方法，它整个都是异质的，异株可培育出新品系。再说，中医的许多学术内容有着浓厚的“元”(源)性质，若以新视野作出审视，常能拓展出新观点、新内容。就象一部《易经》，数千年来皓首研讨者无以计数，但每代人潜心研究下去总会增添新意，即使时至今天，亦未到尽头；又如一本《内经》，若以发展的观点对待，也总能不断推衍诠释出新思想、新论点。当然，要使这种拓展有现实意义，则必须持有正确的研究态度和科学的分析方法。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　We believe that Chinese medicine is just the old, traditional; new, energetic. For Western medicine, because, out of sight, it is remote and heterogeneous, different strains can produce new strains. Besides, many of the intellectual content of traditional Chinese medicine for a touch of the "meta" (source), if a new vision to look at, often developing new ideas, new content. Just like a movie of the book, hoary head researchers not to count for thousands of years, but each adds new generations of painstaking research association, even today, has not come up to the end; a copy of the Sutra, if treated with the viewpoint of development, Always keep tuiyan to convey new ideas, new arguments. Of course, to make this outreach relevant, you must hold the correct attitude and scientific methods of research.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">103</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>一、现时代：医学生存的新的时空背景
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>１．Modern medicine survival of new spatial and temporal context  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">104</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　其实，不仅中医，整个医学都有一个拓展发展空间的问题。而关于中医发展的讨论，也只有纳入世界医学发展的总趋势之中，并结合文化母体（指中国文化）的演变作出考察，才有其实际意义。在我们看来，世界范围无论是医学模式更替的呐喊，还是关于医学目标、目的的讨论，或者“进化医学”的提出，全科医学的复兴，抑或是发达国家正在进行的，举步维艰却又不得不继续的医疗保险制度之改革，都昭示一点：世界医学正处于发展转折之中。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　In fact, not only Chinese, expanding the development space of medicine as a whole has a problem. Discussion on the development of traditional Chinese medicine, only incorporated into the general trend of development of world medicine, combined with the cultural matrix (Chinese culture) to study the evolution of, its practical significance. In our view, either shout of medical model change in the world, and a discussion on medical goals, objectives, or "evolutionary medicine" suggested that the revival of general practice, or whether it is being carried out by developed countries, hobbled but had to continue reform of the medical insurance system, were a sign of a point: medicine in the world were in their turn.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">105</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　很难用一句话来概括当今西方主体医学的总特征，或者可以权且将其视为治“病”的知识技术体系。它看重的是生物结构上的一个个具体的异常（病），采取的也主要是生物的、理化的手段，目的是最大限度地修复这种异常（治愈疾病）。这一切，都是基于还原论所培育的结构至上主义。在过去的一个世纪中，它在控制微生物所致的传染病及营养缺乏等疾病中，取得了巨大的成功，以致于在上世纪中后叶一度让人们对医学充满必胜信念，误以为循此思路，可逐个攻克现存的疾病问题，最终进入人人无病康寿的“自由王国”。然而，几十年来的医学发展却不尽如人意，对于现在危害最甚的常见病的“攻克”，人们一次次败下阵来，现在对这些疾病谈“攻克”问题，已显得过于狂妄。人们开始谦虚了，或低下头沉思起来．．．．．．遂有了变革医学观，更替医学模式，调整医学方向，重新确立医学目的等新主张。而一味依赖技术手段来解决医学问题，使医生沦为技术设备或药物“侍从”的同时，巨大的经济压力也使得整个社会不堪重负。更遗憾的是，即使在欧美这些发达国家，在纯生物医学这个无底洞里投下的巨额资金，并没有解决旧的疾病问题（例如，美国的癌症 10 万人死亡数，从上个世纪 30 年代至 80 年代中期，还以每 10 年 5％～7％的比例攀升，糖尿病的发病和死亡数上升更快），新的棘手病症更是蜂拥而至。因此，“进化医学”开始走俏。对于这些新的学术思潮人们可以作出多种解释，但有一点是无法回避的，即世界医学发展的大趋势、总目标及主导思想和具体思路等，都将被迫而且理应作出某些调整或优化。在我们看来，这种调整将是多方面的，仅就其关注的视野而言，应从只关心病（生物结构异常），回归到既关心人又关心他的病。这虽已是千余年的老生常谈，但它的底蕴和意义人们直至今天仍不见得能完全洞察。很显然，即使明天的医学再发达，投入的医疗资源再充足，人还是会生病的；既生了病，许多也只能是有所控制或缓解，而无法根治；这并非是“不可知论”，而是种客观认真的态度。因此，注重防范各类疾病的发生，就成了最佳并且是迫不得已的选择。另则，生产力的进步给人们带来的不仅是些美酒佳肴类的享受，也包括许多与文明结伴而来的麻烦甚或痛苦。所以，有了现代文明病的概念，更有了众多虽尚算不上疾病（生物结构异常意义上的“疾病”），却也已远离了健康的不正常状态，这些，同样是现代医学必须加以关注重视的。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Difficult to use in a Word to sum up today's total feature of the Western medicine, or you can give it as a cure "disease" of information technology system. Interested in biological structure of one specific exception (disease), is mostly taken by biological, physical and chemical means in order to maximize the repair this abnormal (cure). All this is based on restore on the structure of cultivated by the doctrine. In the past century, control of infectious diseases caused by microbial and nutritional deficiency diseases such as, has been a huge success, so that leaves just after the last century people full of triumphalism in medicine, Mistook this idea solves existing problems one by one, and eventually into disease-free for all Consol "realm". However, decades of medical development is unsatisfactory, for now the most common causes of "conquering", people again and again failed to, for these diseases now talk about "conquering" issue has become too arrogant. People started modest, or lowered his head in thought ... ... Hence changes in medicine, to replace medical model, adjust the medical direction and new ideas, such as the re-establishment of medical purpose. And simply rely on technology to solve medical problems, Technical device or drug that doctors become "servants" at the same time, overwhelmed with enormous economic pressures also make society as a whole. More regrets of is, even in Europe these developed, in pure bio medical this hole in voted Xia of huge funds, and no settlement old of disease problem (such as, United States of cancer 100,000 people death number, from last century 30 generation to 80 generation medium-term, also to each 10 years 5%~7% of proportion climbed, diabetes of onset and death number rose faster), new of tricky illness more is flocked. Thus, "evolutionary medicine" started to tempt. The new academic thought to many interpretations could be made, but one thing is unavoidable, namely the world development trend, the overall goal of medicine and philosophy and the specific ideas, will be forced to and should make some adjustments or tuning. In our opinion, such adjustments would be manifold, just for the view of its concerns, should only care about disease (abnormal biological structures), the return to both care for people and concerned about his condition. It's already a thousand years old, but its implication and significance until today still may not be able to complete the insight. It is clear that even if tomorrow's medicine is developed, invested sufficient medical resources, People will still get sick, both sick, many can only be controlled or mitigated, and no cure; it is not a "agnosticism", but objective attitude. Therefore, pay attention to preventing various diseases, it has become the best and is a last resort option. Also, advances in productivity brought not only the enjoyment of food and wine classes, also includes a number of civilizations in a group of trouble or pain. So, the modern concept of diseases of civilization, although many are still cannot be considered a disease (bio-structural abnormalities in the sense of "disease"), but also away from the unhealthy state of health, which, Likewise, modern medicine must concern seriously.  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">106</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　80 年代初起，人们在反思中提出了健康与疾病之间存在着“第三状态”，或曰“中间状态”、“游离状态”、“灰色状态”等的观点。尽管提法有所不同，所指却基本相似，都是指两者之间的非病非健康状态。这些都反映出了“过程论”的观念，正确地把健康和疾病理解为一个相互联系的过程的两端。近来，人们又主张以“亚健康”来概括这些状态，或称“次健康”状态。并认为：注重亚(次)健康，着力在此领域进行深耕细作，正是发掘中医学潜在优势，拓展中医学术新的生存空间的重要一环，它不仅将给中医学术的发展带来勃勃生机，而且必将促进整个世界医学的调整与发展。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　The beginning of the 80 people reflection exist between health and illness are presented in "third State", or "intermediate state", "free", "grey" perspective. Although formulations vary, the meaning is essentially similar, refers to non-disease health between the two. These reflect a "process" concept, properly understood as an interconnected health and disease processes at both ends. More recently, advocates of the "sub-healthy" summed up the status or "health" status. And that: focus on Asia (times) health, focus on this area of spade husbandry, Explore the medical potential advantages and expand TCM new and important part of the living space, which not only will bring vitality to the development of TCM academic, and will promote the adjustment and development of the world medicine.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">107</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>二、注重状态调整的中医学
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>２．Focus on adjustment of status in traditional Chinese medicine 
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">108</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　许多人学习中医之初，可能会听到一些资深的西医专家说：中医学不是治病的，并质问道：中医究竟有哪些具体的病的概念，确切地说能治什么病？也有中医人士会与之力争，总结出中医是辨证论治的，治证与治病相结合，将是中西医结合的理想模式。这些反驳总有点自我解嘲之嫌。其实站在一个新的角度思考问题，也许会豁然开朗。的确，中医主要不是治“病”的（指西医认为的“病”），她所着眼的主要是不同的生理反应类型（体质）与病理反应状态（证型）。而这不仅仅是中医学的特点（并非是缺陷），也正是现代医学在调整发展中亟需努力加以开垦的处女地。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Many people to learn traditional Chinese medicine early, you may hear some senior Western expert said: medicine is not a cure, and asked: exactly what are the specific concept of traditional Chinese medicine, exactly what can cure disease? With which the Chinese people will also strive to summed is the treatment based on syndrome differentiation of traditional Chinese medicine, treatment of syndrome and treatment of combined would be the ideal model of integrative medicine. Counter somehow suspected of Teresa Teng. Standing in a new perspective, might suddenly see the light. Indeed, mainly traditional Chinese medicine is not a cure "disease" (referring to Western medicine believe that "disease"), She aimed primarily physiological reaction of different types (physical) and the pathological condition (syndromes). And it's not just the characteristics of traditional Chinese medicine (not bug) is needed in the development of modern medicine also trying to reclaim Virgin territory.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">109</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　很长一段时间以来，一谈起医学的功能，人们大多会毫不犹豫地认定是“治病”。这的确不错，也正因为这一点，早先人们因此被诘难后才会感到不舒服。然而，从今天的角度，或者同时结合中国传统医学的观点，对医学的目的和功能作出全新的考虑，可见过去对医学功能的这种认定是有明显欠缺的，以此来定义医学的意义，只能说是跛腿的。早在《素问》时代，古代医贤就认定：医学的目的，首先是“消患于未兆”，“济羸劣以获安”（均见《素问》序），其次才是治病祛疾。所谓“未兆”，即未有显著疾病征兆之时；所谓“羸劣”，即虚损或不太健康，但不一定是有病的状态。而这些，正是今人所说的次健康或亚健康状态。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　For a long time now, starts talking about the medical function, most people will not hesitate to assume the "cure". All well and good, also because of this, people were earlier questioned before they feel uncomfortable. However, from today's perspective, or combined with traditional Chinese medicine point of view, their new consideration of the purpose and function of the medicine, visible past the medical function of such a finding is clearly lacking, in order to define the meaning of medical, can only be described as a lame leg. As early as the era of the Su Wen, the ancient sages decided that: the purpose of medicine, beginning with "extinction is not" "Chai win bad for Ann" (see order of the plain questions), followed by treatment of disease. The so-called "no", that is, when there are significant signs of illness; the so-called "win bad", that is, wasting or not very healthy, but not necessarily in the diseased State. And these, divination is that the minor's health or sub-health status.  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">110</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>三、干预病前状态——医学的新需求
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>３．Intervention before disease state-- New demand for medical  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">111</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　从另一角度而言，一资深的临床内科医师，一定能认可这一点：除一般的感染性疾病外，绝大多数被西医学明确界定为“病”的器质性病变，一旦发展到出现了明显临床症状，促使患者寻求医师参与纠治时，十有八九已无法完全治愈，充其量只能有效地加以控制、缓解或防范其进一步恶化；或者即使是能“治愈”，通常也需付出极大的、甚至无可补救的代价（包括手术切除等）。且不说这一治疗控制过程正让人们承担着越来越昂贵的费用，人们还必须时时为这些已形成的病变提心吊胆，接受“煎熬”，防范其随时可能发生的恶化；或者每天大把大把地吞下或多或少带有某些毒副作用的治疗性的合成药物。因此，这显然不是最佳选择，也不是聪明的上策，更无法满足现代社会发展对医学提出的新要求。换个角度，时至今日，人们已经有可能采取更为聪明的方式方法，对疾病问题作出超前的应对，那就是注重它的临床前期，关注非病非健康而又有可能趋向于“病”的“未病”状态。这种状态就是本文前面所说的所谓次健康、亚健康、第三状态等。研究已经表明，现在临床疾病中占前几位的疾病，除肿瘤的临床前期人们还所知不多，很难及早作出把握外，心血管、脑血管、呼吸、消化系统和代谢性疾病等都有一个较为缓慢而渐进的发展过程，这一过程正好给人们采取针对性的防范措施预留了比较宽裕的操作空间，且对其发展的大体的阶段性特点也已略知二三。因此，借助现代诊察手段，有充分的可能在临床出现明确症状，出现确凿的病理改变之前（亦即次健康、亚健康状态），便作出针对性的防范。即使再扩大一些，或再往前追溯，一些常见的、一时难以明确其临床病理意义的症状，如慢性疲劳、反复容易感冒、慢性咽痛、情绪低落、睡眠障碍等，人们也都能借助中医，作出些有效的应对。因此，在操作技术上，把关注的重点转向次健康状态，已有了现实的可行性。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　From another angle, a senior of clinical medicine physician, must can recognized this is: except General of infection sexual disease outside, most was West medical clear defined for "disease" of organic lesions, once development to appeared has obviously clinical symptoms, led patients sought physician participation correcting treatment Shi, nine times out of has cannot completely cure, at best only effective to be control, and mitigation or against its further deteriorated; or even is can "cure", usually also needed paid great of, and Even irreversible costs (including surgery). Apart from this treatment process are giving people more and more and more expensive cost of People must also be constantly to these existing lesions of nervous with the "suffering" to prevent any possible deterioration; or swallowing lots every day, more or less with some of the toxic and side effects of treatment of synthetic drugs. So, clearly this is not the best choice, nor clever way, unable to meet the new demands on medical development in modern society. From a different perspective, to this day, people are likely to adopt a more clever ways, leading to disease problems to deal with, it is focusing on preclinical, focus on non-health and non-disease risk tends to "disease" and "disease" State. This State is mentioned earlier in this article called health, sub-health, third, and so on. Research has indicates that, now clinical disease in the accounted for Qian several of disease, except tumor of clinical early people also by known not more, hard early made grasp outside, cardiovascular, and brain vascular, and breathing, and digestive system and metabolism sexual disease, are has a more slow and progressive of development process, this a process just to people take pointed of against measures reserved has comparison plenty of of operation space, and on its development of General of staged features also has slightly known two or three. Therefore, the use of modern diagnostic tools, there is ample might be present a clear clinical symptoms, Before they produce pathological changes of hard (aka health, sub-health status), targeted at prevention. Even if expanded, or go back any farther, some common, hard to identify their clinicopathological significance of symptoms, such as chronic fatigue, recurrent colds, chronic sore throat, depression, sleep disorders, people also can use TCM, an effective response. Therefore, operational skills, health focus of concern has been the practical feasibility. 
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">112</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>四、治病，调整状态－—现代医学之两翼 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>４．Treatment, adjusting status—2 sides of modern medical studies
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">113</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　生老病死是一个连续的过程，各不同阶段自有其一定的阶段特殊性：健康、次健康、病态、死亡同样是一种连续的过程，各个阶段亦有着一定的征兆或特点可言。现代医学借助了还原方法，重点剖析了具体病态的多方面特征，并以线性方程的思想，着重针对病因或对症治，在较为单纯的生物性疾病的预防方面取得了巨大的成功，也锻造了医学就是“治病”这一根深蒂固的社会观念。中医学显然走的是另一条路，早先在实用理性的规范下，它既没有可能敦促医生去深究一个个病的确切病因及具体的病理形态学改变，也没有可能促使医学将兴趣投入在这方面。它指引医家，借助望闻问切、司外揣内、比类取象等传统方法，仔仔细细地寻觅求诊者所表现的偏离健康的蛛丝马迹（“阴阳偏颇”），并结合中医学对生命的独特理解，进行分析判断，然后采用纯自然的方药或针灸推拿等作出纠治，冀能使其重新恢复常态（“以平为期”）。因此，中医内科学中绝大多数病名（也许仅“消渴”除外），只是一个症状名词，或一组临床表现。它强调辨证，其实质就是辨病理反应状态；它所讲的体质，又可理解为生理反应类型及不同的生理状态。可见，中医学是注重“状态”的。而且，它不仅重视病理状态，也关注理论上偏离了正常（阴阳平和）但尚未发展成病理的种种不同状态。我们体质研究中所注意到的除正常体质外的不同体质类型，其实也就是种种不同的亚(次)健康类型的组合。在我们看来，不仅辨证（辨体质）是注重状态的，治疗方药也不例外。中药大致可分成两大类，一类是对症或治病的，如白头翁止痢、麻黄止喘；更多的则是什么病也不治，什么病都可用的（当然必须符合相应的指征），比如人参、黄芪、当归、熟地等，它们治什么病？什么特异性的“病”也不治，但相应的虚损状态都可以用，可见，它们主要是调整状态的。是气虚态就可用前两味，偏血虚就可用后两味。即使没病，只要机体处于虚弱状态，也可以用。而后者，正是我们今天所说的次健康、亚健康状态。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Birth is a continuous process, each has its own particularity a certain stage at different stages: health, health, sickness, and death is a continuous process, each stage also has some signs or features to speak of. Modern medicine through the restore method, and analyzed various characteristics of the specific pathological, and linear thought, focuses on the causes and symptomatic treatment, in terms of relatively simple biological disease prevention has been a great success, also forged a medicine is "cure" this deeply ingrained social attitudes. TCM is going the other way, earlier in the practical criterion of rationality, It is neither possible to urge doctors to get to the bottom of the exact cause of the disease and the specific pathological changes, without any input in this regard might prompt medical interest. It guidelines medical home, with utilizes electrocardiographs, and Division outside hides within, and than class take like, traditional method, carefully to looking for attendance who by performance of deviated from health of traces ("yin and Yang biased"), and combines TCM on life of unique understands, for analysis judgment, then used pure natural of prescription or acupuncture massage, made correcting treatment, JI can makes its again recovery normal ("to flat for"). Therefore, The vast majority of Chinese internal medicine (perhaps just "Diabetes"), is just a noun, or a group of clinical manifestations. It emphasizes differentiation, its essence is to distinguish the pathological state; it is about physical fitness, can be understood as the type and physiological responses of different physiological States. Visible, traditional Chinese medicine is focused on "status". Moreover, it not only attention to pathological conditions, as well as theoretically deviated from the normal (peace of yin and Yang) but have not yet developed into a pathology of various different States. We have noted physical fitness research in addition to normal physical body constitution types in different, or indeed of many different sub-(sub-) combinations of health types. In our opinion, not only the dialectic (syndrome differentiation of Constitution) is focused on the status, treatment prescriptions are no exception. Traditional Chinese medicine can be broadly divided into two main categories: one is symptomatic or curative, as bulbul dysentery, ephedra zhichuan; died more then what it is, what is available (of course must conform to the corresponding indications), such as ginseng, Astragalus membranaceus and Angelica sinensis, Radix rehmanniae, they cure disease? What specific "disease" died, but wasting status can be used, we can see that they were mainly tuning status. Is the Qi State in the previous two, partial deficiency of available two flavor. If not, as long as the body is in a weak State, Can also be used. The latter is what we today call health, sub-health status.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">114</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　很显然，从发展的角度来看，理想的现代医学，必须同时兼顾治病和调整状态这两大方面，确实生了病，自需调动一切积极措施，治疗疾病，修复生物学上的异常；如处于病前状态，病后虚弱或失调状态，以及偏离健康的种种状态，则又当采取种种手段，特别是中药学的一系列有效经验，加以纠正和调整。可以说，治病和调整状态，将成为未来医学的重要两翼。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>Apparently, from development of angle see, ideal of modern medical, must while balance cure and adjustment state this two big aspects, does health has disease, since needed mobilization all active measures, treatment disease, repair biology Shang of exception; as is disease Qian State, disease Hou weak or disorders State, and deviated from health of various State, is and Dang take various means, especially TCM learn of series effective experience, be corrected and adjustment. It can be said that heal and adjust status, will become important wing of the medicine of the future.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">115</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>五、未雨绸缪，拓展学术生存新空间
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>５．Prepare for rainy days - expanding the space for new academic survival   
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">116</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　这里，必须指出的是，我们提出亚(次)健康，并分析指出原先中医包含有这方面的临症特点，并非是新瓶装旧酒，用时髦的“次健康”概念来包装中医固有的，十分成熟有偏于陈旧的诸如气虚、血虚、痰湿、郁证等概念，而是高屋建瓴地提出一个重要的新命题。社会的发展迫切需要医学拓展其视野，不仅关注病，更应解决病前的次健康状态，甚至优化群体的体质，提高人群的健康水准。而在这一方面，中医学有许多潜在优势，隐含于从理论观念一直到诊疗操作，乃至方药食疗等中。若我们以超前的战略眼光努力地致力于发掘、提升中医学在这些方面的潜在优势，那将会给中医学的生存，拓展出一片广袤而又前景灿烂的领域。当然，我们并不认为中医学中关于次健康的内容已十分完备，只须发掘一下即可，恰恰相反，中医学的相关内容是粗糙和零碎的，有待于大大充实和提炼，使之系统、细化，且深化。尽管如此，有许多优势却是不用谦虚地加以推让的，包括注重状态的动态分析把握，运用两分法（阴阳）的层层剖析，尤其是在调整纠治中，借助纯自然的方药或非药物自然疗法等，并由此积累了丰富的经验，这些都是应对亚(次)健康状态的无价之宝。 
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　Here, must pointed out that of is, we made Asia (times) health, and analysis pointed out that originally TCM contains has this aspects of Pro syndrome features, is not is new bottled old wine, with fashionable of "times health" concept to packaging TCM inherent of, is mature has partial Yu old of such as Qi, and deficiency, and sputum wet, and Yu card, concept, but strategically advantageous position to made a important of new proposition. Community development urgently needs to expand its horizons in medicine, focused not only on illness, should be resolved before the State of health, optimal group of physical fitness, improving the standard of health of the population. In this context, traditional Chinese medicine has many potential advantages, Concepts implicit in the theory until the clinic operations, as well as prescription diet. If our efforts to advance the strategic commitment to discover, improve in these potential advantages of traditional Chinese medicine, that would have put the survival of traditional Chinese medicine, developed a vast and promising field. Of course, we do not believe that traditional Chinese medicine on health content has been very extensive, just discovered you can, on the contrary, relevant elements of the traditional Chinese medicine is rough and fragmentary, remains to be greatly enriched and refined, system, refined, and deepened. That said, there are many advantages but is not humble enough to be inflicting, Included a focus on dynamic analysis to grasp and use dichotomies (yin and Yang) layer-by-layer analysis, in particular adjustment of the correction, using purely natural drugs or non-drug natural therapies, and has accumulated a wealth of experience, these are Asian (times) health status of priceless treasures.  
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">117</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">
<p>　　在现时代的中医发展中，我们有过太多的遗憾了。以往，我们总是等西医学某个观点、某个理论、某个学科接近成熟才想起“中医早已有之”从而拼命地加以考据论证，这样做，虽无不可，但充其量只能暂时平衡一下心态，于学科发展终究无大益。也许，随着 21 世纪的到来，人们会越来越关注次健康问题，这次发展中医、拓展生存空间的机遇，无论如何不应该再错过了。
</p>
</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">
<p>　　In the development of modern Chinese medicine, we have too many regrets. The past, we always Western medicine such as an idea, a theory, a subject close to be mature, "medicine has long been" trying to be historically accurate demonstration, which, though there is no reason, but at best only a temporary balance of mind, on development of no great use after all. Perhaps, with the advent of the 21st century, people will increasingly focus on health issues, the development of traditional Chinese medicine, to expansion of surviving space of opportunity, and in any event should not be missed.
</p>
</td></tr>
